channel.title: Project SJ Released!
channel.description:
[center][size=14pt]Project SJ Released By Shane & Jon[/center]
[center]Just so people dont get confused eddie2000111 was the account i always used and my real name is shane [/center]
The reason why we have decide to release this is that we dont have the time anymore to kill it running and we had all of the fun from this project that there possibly was to of been had, it has been a great learning experience, and now it is time to give back to the community so other people can have as much fun with this as we did.
This means Out of common respect if you use this base, it would be nice for some recognition with a reply, or some Thanks. And if you release a server with this as a base, some credits would be nice :D
Credits: Insidiax Source (not the new one i used the old one and have worked on it since august)
For anyone thinking this is the v2 of insidiax this is not becasue i have proof that this was done before insidiax v2 come out
http://projectsj.freeforums.org/new-skill-interface-look-update-soon-to-be-released-t42.html
[center][size=18pt]The Features Include...[/size] -Custom Ranks With All Crowns Fully Working -New Skill Interface -Basic Staff List -Working Cash Orb -Loyalty Titles With a Few Custom ones -Fading Hitmarks -Added Working Leech Spec and ALL Saps Curses. -Combat Icons Next to Damage -All Important Summoning Special Attacks -10Man "Raid" Style Bosses -Nomad -Introduction of Red Dragons, Very Active Pking -Wilderness Revernants -Elite Slayer Tasks -FULLY working Overloads 100% RS -39 Jad Waves, Custom -Unique Custom Home -Dragonfireshield works 100% Charging! -100% Working pvp armours ( Statius, Vesta, Zuriel and Morrigan)! -PKP Shops -Even More NPC Anims Added -Player Owned Shops -Sarabrew doesnt drain stats when overloaded -PERFECT Bridding / Switching -Fully Webclient Ready -Soulwars Cape & More Items Added -Torva, Korasi, Primal (With Effect's) -317 Classic RS Graphics -NEW RS AUTOCAST FEATURE -Dungeoneering Skillcape Emotes, Chaotic Shields -NO DUPES, ALL BUGS FIXED -602 Animations, 602 GFX, 474 Maps, 614 Items, 317 Characters -Enhanced GFX Rendering Looks Smoother! -FUNPK Area -Perfect Constitution x10 Hits and HP -Very accurate Special Calcs for PvP Server -Near Flawless Combat System -Perfect RS Chaotic Crossbow -Real RS Dung Teleport /w Kinship Ring -Dungeoneering -Working and Completely Custom PK Skill (exp from winning in wild) [/center]
[center] [b][size=12pt][color=brown][u]Player Rights [/u] Trail Mod - 7 Mod - 1 Trail Admin - 8 Head Of Staff (Also Admin) - 2 Owner - 6 Donator - 4 Server Sponsor -5 Verteran - 9[/size][/center]
[center] [b][size=10pt][color=brown][u]Loyalty Titles [/u] 1: "Lord" 2: "Sir" 3: "Lionheart" 4: "Desperado" 5: "Bandito" 6: "King" 7: "Big Cheese" 8: "Wunderkind" 9: "Crusader" 10: "Overlord" 11: "Bigwig" 12: "Count" 13: "Duderino" 14: "Hell Raiser" 15: "Baron" 16: "Duke" 17: "Lady" 18: "Dame" 19: "Dudette" 20: "Baroness" 21: "Countess" 22: "Overlordess" 23: "Duchess" 24: "Queen" 25: "Mod" 26: "Admin" 27: "Server Sponcer" 28: "Owner" [/size][/center]

If you download the cache from the above mirror, then you will need to put the cache in your C: drive for it to work :)
I DO GIVE PERMISSION FOR THIS TO BE RE-RELEASED!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Good Luck to anybody planning on using this base or releasing this, and i wish for everybody the best of luck! If everyone puts together their work when they are finished then the community will progress as a unit, so keep it going
If you would like any help and im on then i will be happy to help you if i have the spare time[/center]
